  "doc_id": "1569",
  "text": "To compare to the concurrent model in [CITATION_1] , we consider a setting in which we exploit additional training data. We adopt the same pre-training strategy as [CITATION_2] , that is we pretrain a monocular pose estimation network on the COCO dataset [CITATION_3] , and fine-tune jointly on Human3.6M and MPII [CITATION_4] datasets. We then simply use these pre-trained weights to initialize our network. We also report results for [CITATION_5] , which trains its detector jointly on MPII and Human3.6M. The results are reported in Table 4 .",
